2014年6月8日，10名武装分子携带自动武器、火箭筒、自杀式背心和[[手榴弹|手榴弹]]，袭击了位于[[卡拉奇|卡拉奇]]的[[真纳国际机场|真纳国际机场]]。事件造成包括武装分子在内的36人遇害、18人受伤。[[巴基斯坦塔利班运动|塔利班]]承认为袭击事件负责。袭击者来自与[[基地组织|基地组织]]有关联的[[乌兹别克斯坦伊斯兰运动|乌兹别克斯坦伊斯兰运动]]（IMU），和塔利班有密切合作<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2014/06/11/world/asia/pakistan-karachi-airport-attacks/ |title=Drone strike in Pakistan days after airport attack, sources say - CNN.com |accessdate=2014-06-14 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304235629/http://edition.cnn.com/2014/06/11/world/asia/pakistan-karachi-airport-attacks/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。塔利班后来证实这次袭击，係該组织与IMU的联合行动，而IMU则独立承担了在袭击中提供战斗机的责任<ref name="Zarb"/>。

== 背景 ==
真纳国际机场是[[巴基斯坦|巴基斯坦]]最大型、最繁忙的机场，[[巴基斯坦国际航空|巴基斯坦国际航空]]公司的枢纽所在。众多国际和国内航班每天在机场中转。本次袭击是该机场近几年来的第一起大规模事件，1986年此地曾发生过[[泛美航空73号班机劫机事件|泛美航空73号班机劫机事件]]<ref name="tribune"/><ref name="tribune3">{{cite news|url=http://tribune.com.pk/story/719575/terror-woes-a-dark-night-for-the-aviation-sector/|title=Terror woes: A dark night for the aviation sector|work=Express Tribune|date=10 June 2014|accessdate=10 June 2014|archive-date=2014-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140621084431/http://tribune.com.pk/story/719575/terror-woes-a-dark-night-for-the-aviation-sector/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2011年年初，类似的袭击发生在卡拉奇迈赫兰海军航空基地。武装分子还在2012年袭击了巴基斯坦西北部城市[[白沙瓦|白沙瓦]]的[[巴查·汗国际机场|巴查·汗国际机场]]<ref name="guardian"/>。

== 过程 ==
袭击于6月8日上午11点20分开始，持续到翌日凌晨4点<ref name="bp" />。十名持自动武器、手榴弹、[[火箭推进榴弹|火箭推进榴弹]]及其他爆炸物的武装分子，乘坐面包车突击机场安全检查站，直奔货运码头<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nation.com.pk/national/09-Jun-2014/karachi-airport-attacked-indian-weapons-recovered-from-the-terrorists |title=Karachi Airport attacked; Indian weapons recovered from the terrorists |publisher=Nation.com.pk |date= |accessdate=2014-06-11 |archive-date=2014-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140611112811/http://www.nation.com.pk/national/09-Jun-2014/karachi-airport-attacked-indian-weapons-recovered-from-the-terrorists |dead-url=no }}</ref> 。武装分子穿着机场安全部队制服伪装成保安员，利用假身份证进入机场<ref name=aje />，一些人还穿着自杀式炸弹背心。一位巴基斯坦高级情报官员称，有些武装分子曾试图劫持一架飞机，但以失败告终<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/jun/08/karachi-airport-attacked-militants-pakistan|title=Heavy fighting at Karachi airport as militants and security forces clash|publisher=theguardian.com|accessdate=2014-06-21|archive-date=2014-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140626181046/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/jun/08/karachi-airport-attacked-militants-pakistan|dead-url=no}}</ref>。90分钟，数百名[[特种部队|特种部队]]突击队员抵达现场，与武装分子交火<ref name=wapo />。据报道，武装分子起初控制了机场的[[停机坪|停机坪]]和跑道。5小时后，围困行动正式结束，期间十名武装分子，有八名被突击队击毙，两名自爆身亡<ref name=wapo>{{cite news|last1=Craig|first1=Tim|title=9 killed in attack on key Pakistani airport|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/asia_pacific/pakistan-airport-attack-kills-5/2014/06/08/9fbbbe2a-ef46-11e3-914c-1fbd0614e2d4_story.html?hpid=z1|accessdate=8 June 2014|work=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]|date=2014-06-08|archive-date=2014-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140613081850/http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/asia_pacific/pakistan-airport-attack-kills-5/2014/06/08/9fbbbe2a-ef46-11e3-914c-1fbd0614e2d4_story.html?hpid=z1|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=ur-Rehman|first1=Zia|last2=Masood|first2=Salman|title=Gunmen Attack Karachi Airport, Killing at Least 6|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2014/06/09/world/asia/deadly-attack-karachi-international-airport.html|accessdate=8 June 2014|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|date=2014-06-08|archive-date=2014-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140612000923/http://www.nytimes.com/2014/06/09/world/asia/deadly-attack-karachi-international-airport.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。10名武装分子、11名特种兵、2名游骑兵、1名信德省警察、4名巴基斯坦航空雇员（包括两名高级飞机工程师<ref name="tribune3"/>），共36人在事件中遇害<ref name="tribune">{{cite web|url=http://tribune.com.pk/story/719242/four-security-personnel-injured-in-attack-on-karachi-airport/|title=Live: Search operation underway after firing near Karachi airport|publisher=The Express Tribune|accessdate=2014-06-21|archive-date=2014-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140618163800/http://tribune.com.pk/story/719242/four-security-personnel-injured-in-attack-on-karachi-airport/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。至少18名保安人员在袭击中负伤被送往阿巴西·沙希德医院<ref name="bp">{{cite web|title=Attack on Karachi Airport in Pakistan airport leaves over 23 dead|url=http://news.biharprabha.com/2014/06/attack-on-karachi-airport-in-pakistan-airport-leaves-over-23-dead/|work=IANS|publisher=news.biharprabha.com|accessdate=9 June 2014|archive-date=2014-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140819121038/http://news.biharprabha.com/2014/06/attack-on-karachi-airport-in-pakistan-airport-leaves-over-23-dead/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。被烧得面目全非的七具尸体，在随后的28小时救援行动中，被移送至机场的冷藏设施<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dawn.com/news/1111784/seven-bodies-recovered-from-karachi-airports-cold-storage-facility |title=Seven bodies recovered from Karachi airport’s cold-storage facility |publisher=Dawn.Com |date= |accessdate=2014-06-11 |archive-date=2014-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140610203522/http://www.dawn.com/news/1111784/seven-bodies-recovered-from-karachi-airports-cold-storage-facility |dead-url=no }}</ref>。巴基斯坦航空三架飞机（[[波音747|波音747]]、[[空客A310|空客A310]]、[[波音777|波音777]]）和沙欣航空两架飞机遭损。巴基斯坦航空起先未详细说明飞机受损部位，但有消息称，飞机直接被子弹或弹片击中<ref name="initial damage">{{Cite web |url=http://www.dawn.com/news/1111870 |title=Attack causes heavy losses to airlines, traders - Newspaper - DAWN.COM |accessdate=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2014-06-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140621014555/http://www.dawn.com/news/1111870 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。两个存储将被出口的进口货运仓库化为灰烬，给贸易商和进口商蒙受巨大损失。伊斯帕哈尼机库遭手榴弹攻击<ref name="dawn">{{Cite web |url=http://www.dawn.com/news/1111397 |title=TTP claims attack on Karachi airport - Pakistan - DAWN.COM |accessdate=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2014-06-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140621153950/http://www.dawn.com/news/1111397 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。袭击事件发生后，机场被清空并移交至民航局和机场安全部队<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dawn.com/news/1111581 |title=Karachi airport handed over to CAA, open for operations - Pakistan - DAWN.COM |accessdate=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2014-06-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140625181342/http://www.dawn.com/news/1111581 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[卡拉奇|卡拉奇]]工商会会长阿卜杜拉·扎基对袭击后的安全形势和对经济的影响，持保留意见：“局势的不断恶化，可从最近的机场袭击中看出城市总体上不安全。目前形势上，不仅国内游客因为机场袭击的缘故而不敢访问卡拉奇，还使得外国人由于电视频道对此类事件的报道泛滥远离巴基斯坦，尤其是商人和投资者<ref name="initial damage"/>。”

== 调查 ==
信德省别动队总干事阿赫塔尔上将提供初步报告，声称武装分子或为[[乌兹别克人|乌兹别克人]]<ref name="tribune"/>。塔利班于6月11日证实该消息，[[乌兹别克斯坦伊斯兰运动|乌兹别克斯坦伊斯兰运动]]在本次袭击中提供直升机支援<ref name="Uzbeks">{{Cite web |url=http://www.thenews.com.pk/article-150430-IMU,-Al-Qaeda-affiliate-claims-its-fighters-attacked-Karachi-airport |title=IMU, Al-Qaeda affiliate claims its fighters attacked Karachi airport - thenews.com.pk |accessdate=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2014-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140611181943/http://www.thenews.com.pk/article-150430-IMU%2C-Al-Qaeda-affiliate-claims-its-fighters-attacked-Karachi-airport |dead-url=no }}</ref>。内政部部长乔杜里·尼萨尔·阿里·汗表示，国内外势力共同参与了袭击<ref name="dawn2">{{Cite web |url=http://www.dawn.com/news/1111601 |title=Nisar sees foreign, local elements involved in terror attacks - Pakistan - DAWN.COM |accessdate=2014-06-22 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304030813/http://www.dawn.com/news/1111601 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，联邦新闻部长拉希德·穆沙拉夫也认为境外势力策划袭击<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.thenews.com.pk/article-150231-Pervez-Rashid-sees-foreign-hand-behind-Karachi-airport-attack-- |title=Pervez Rashid sees foreign hand behind Karachi airport attack - thenews.com.pk |accessdate=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2014-06-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140619182703/http://www.thenews.com.pk/article-150231-Pervez-Rashid-sees-foreign-hand-behind-Karachi-airport-attack-- |dead-url=no }}</ref>。巴基斯坦官方在[[阿富汗|阿富汗]]境内发现反巴基斯坦武装分子的窝点后，阿富汗驻巴基斯坦大使被传唤<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.khaama.com/pakistan-summons-afghan-ambassador-following-attack-on-karachi-airport-6199 |title=Pakistan summons Afghan ambassador following attack on Karachi airport - Khaama Press (KP) {{!}} Afghan News Agency |accessdate=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2014-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140612133304/http://www.khaama.com/pakistan-summons-afghan-ambassador-following-attack-on-karachi-airport-6199 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

有媒体援引巴基斯坦别动队的消息，称从被击毙的武装分子身上缴获印度制枪支或弹药<ref name="IB">{{Cite web |url=http://www.ibtimes.com/militant-attack-karachi-airport-pakistan-claims-23-lives-least-14-wounded-1595961 |title=Militant Attack On Karachi Airport In Pakistan Claims 23 Lives, At Least 14 Wounded |accessdate=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2014-06-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140613233847/http://www.ibtimes.com/militant-attack-karachi-airport-pakistan-claims-23-lives-least-14-wounded-1595961 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://dunyanews.tv/index.php/en/Pakistan/224751-Karachi-Indianmade-arms-recovered-from-dead-mili Karachi: Indian-made arms recovered from dead militants | Pakistan | Dunya News]</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/militant-attack-on-karachi-airport-four-security-personnel-killed/1/365966.html |title=Karachi's Jinnah International Airport under siege: 11 dead, 2 planes destroyed : World, News - India Today |accessdate=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2016-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160204220423/http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/militant-attack-on-karachi-airport-four-security-personnel-killed/1/365966.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.thenews.com.pk/article-150165-Karachi-airport-under-attack:-five-ASF-men-killed |title=15 killed as terrorists attack Karachi airport - thenews.com.pk |accessdate=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2014-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714222710/http://www.thenews.com.pk/article-150165-Karachi-airport-under-attack%3A-five-ASF-men-killed |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://www.samaa.tv/pakistan/09-Jun-2014/karachi-airport-attack-rangers-says-indian-weapons-recovered ]{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nation.com.pk/national/09-Jun-2014/karachi-airport-attacked-indian-weapons-recovered-from-the-terrorists |title=Karachi Airport attacked; Indian weapons recovered from the terrorists |accessdate=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2014-06-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140622082433/http://www.nation.com.pk/national/09-Jun-2014/karachi-airport-attacked-indian-weapons-recovered-from-the-terrorists |dead-url=no }}</ref>，暗指印度参与在背后参与袭击<ref name=autogenerated1 /><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2014/06/09/world/asia/deadly-attack-karachi-international-airport.html?_r=1 |title=Terrorists Attack Airport in Pakistan, Killing 13 |publisher=The New York Times |date= |accessdate=2014-06-11 |archive-date=2014-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140716153021/http://www.nytimes.com/2014/06/09/world/asia/deadly-attack-karachi-international-airport.html?_r=1 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 。Geo英文频道最先发布信德省别动队总干事，在[[推特|推特]]上发表的关于从现场收缴的印度武器的声明<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/India-Pak-verbal-duel-after-Karachi-airport-siege/articleshow/36272567.cms |title=India-Pak verbal duel after Karachi airport siege - The Times of India |accessdate=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2014-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140612055856/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/India-Pak-verbal-duel-after-Karachi-airport-siege/articleshow/36272567.cms |dead-url=no }}</ref>。另有媒体报道搜索行动期间发现数支印度制“因子-8注射液”。有官员称这些注射液供在前线作战的印度陆军使用，可起到抑制出血的目的。注射液不能在市场上出现。然而，该消息未经巴基斯坦当局证实<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dailytimes.com.pk/national/09-Jun-2014/factor-8-injections-recovered-at-karachi-airport |title=‘Factor-8’ injections recovered at Karachi airport |accessdate=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2014-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140611015034/http://www.dailytimes.com.pk/national/09-Jun-2014/factor-8-injections-recovered-at-karachi-airport |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.samaa.tv/pakistan/09-Jun-2014/karachi-attack-several-made-in-india-injections-recovered |title=Karachi attack: Several made-in-India injections recovered |access-date=2014-06-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140612001036/http://www.samaa.tv/pakistan/09-Jun-2014/karachi-attack-several-made-in-india-injections-recovered |archive-date=2014-06-12 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nation.com.pk/national/09-Jun-2014/indian-army-s-injections-recovered-from-karachi-airport-attackers |title=Indian army’s injections recovered from Karachi airport attackers |accessdate=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2014-06-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140623094742/http://www.nation.com.pk/national/09-Jun-2014/indian-army-s-injections-recovered-from-karachi-airport-attackers |dead-url=no }}</ref>。巴基斯坦议会反对党领袖赛义德·卡苏沙阿呼吁政府就缴获的印度武器，向印度高级议会提出抗议，并要求[[印度政府|印度政府]]解释该问题，他还质疑印度情报机构的作用<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.saach.tv/2014/06/11/india-should-clarify-its-position-over-indian-weapons/ |title=‘India should clarify its position over Indian weapons’ {{!}} Saach.TV |accessdate=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2014-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714162448/http://www.saach.tv/2014/06/11/india-should-clarify-its-position-over-indian-weapons/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://thenewstribe.com/2014/06/11/khursheed-shah-for-indian-explanation-over-karachi-airport-attack/ |title=Khurshid Shah for Indian explanation over Karachi airport attack {{!}} Thenewstribe |accessdate=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2014-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140706192041/http://www.thenewstribe.com/2014/06/11/khursheed-shah-for-indian-explanation-over-karachi-airport-attack/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.pakistantoday.com.pk/2014/06/11/national/mind-asking-india-about-their-guns-with-terrorists/ |title=‘Mind asking India about their guns with terrorists?’ {{!}} Pakistan Today |accessdate=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2014-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714130108/http://www.pakistantoday.com.pk/2014/06/11/national/mind-asking-india-about-their-guns-with-terrorists/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。官方尚未就此事作回应<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.firstpost.com/world/karachi-airport-attack-live-pak-army-says-militants-carried-indian-made-guns-1561631.html |title=Karachi airport attack Live: Miltants had 'Indian' guns, says Pak {{!}} Firstpost |accessdate=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2019-09-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912032857/https://www.firstpost.com/world/karachi-live-taliban-attacks-again-no-casualties-1561631.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=When scare becomes nationalistic pride|url=http://www.thenews.com.pk/Todays-News-6-255305-When-scare-becomes-nationalistic-pride|accessdate=11 June 2014|publisher=The News|date=11 June 2014|archive-date=2014-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140611063524/http://www.thenews.com.pk/Todays-News-6-255305-When-scare-becomes-nationalistic-pride|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|first1=Editorial|title=The aftermath|url=http://www.dailytimes.com.pk/editorial/11-Jun-2014/the-aftermath|accessdate=11 June 2014|publisher=Daily Times|date=11 June 2014|archive-date=2014-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140618131355/http://www.dailytimes.com.pk/editorial/11-Jun-2014/the-aftermath|dead-url=no}}</ref>。巴基斯坦外交部声称，他们正调查袭击中使用的印度武器。官方发言人阿斯拉穆女士表示，巴基斯坦不会在未经调查取证的前提下提出指控<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nation.com.pk/islamabad/13-Jun-2014/use-of-indian-arms-in-karachi-attack-being-probed-fo |title=Use of Indian arms being probed: FO |publisher=The Nation, Pakistan |date=2014-06-14 |accessdate=2014-06-14 |archive-date=2014-06-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140613112612/http://www.nation.com.pk/islamabad/13-Jun-2014/use-of-indian-arms-in-karachi-attack-being-probed-fo |dead-url=no }}</ref>。内政部国际危机处理司表示，在袭击中使用的武器和炸药，或在武装分子冲击机场前，已被运到机场大楼，反映出安保被渗透的漏洞<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dawn.com/news/1111747/ |title=Interior ministry cell had warned of attack on airports, airbases - Pakistan |publisher=Dawn.Com |date= |accessdate=2014-06-11 |archive-date=2014-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140610203011/http://www.dawn.com/news/1111747 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。打击塔利班的第一手信息报告，6月11日在机场警察局提交，领导人法兹鲁拉和发言人沙希德被提及<ref name="FIR">{{Cite web |url=http://www.dawn.com/news/1112018/fir-over-karachi-airport-attack-registered-against-ttp |title=Airport attack: Body of missing ASF man recovered - Pakistan - DAWN.COM |accessdate=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2014-06-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140614202418/http://www.dawn.com/news/1112018/fir-over-karachi-airport-attack-registered-against-ttp |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 后续 ==
袭击发生后，机场停止所有业务，全部航班被分流，人员被疏散。巴基斯坦国际航空在袭击事件后，立即推迟或取消20架航班<ref name="tribune3"/>。巴基斯坦陆军部队在袭击期间部署至机场<ref name=aje>{{cite web|title=Heavy fighting reported at Karachi airport|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/asia/2014/06/heavy-fighting-reported-at-karachi-airport-201468185852200231.html|publisher=[[Al_Jazeera_English|Al Jazeera English]]|accessdate=8 June 2014|date=2014-06-08|archive-date=2014-07-13|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6R2Yfj13O?url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/asia/2014/06/heavy-fighting-reported-at-karachi-airport-201468185852200231.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。行动结束后，巴基斯坦国防部长卡瓦贾穆罕默德·阿西夫表示：“这种恐怖行动不可饶恕，国家将会对这种懦弱的恐怖行动予以回应。那些盘算着策划恐袭的人不会得逞<ref name="guardian">{{Cite web |url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/jun/09/pakistan-taliban-karachi-attack-peace-talks |title=Pakistani Taliban claim Karachi attack and leave peace talks in crisis {{!}} World news {{!}} The Guardian |accessdate=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2014-06-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140620035313/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/jun/09/pakistan-taliban-karachi-attack-peace-talks |dead-url=no }}</ref>。”

《[[卫报|卫报]]》报道称，该机场的保安措施此前遭到批评。把守前往主航站楼的外围道路的卫兵，拿的竟是找矿棒，类似于2013年因涉嫌诈骗被判入狱的吉姆·麦考密克，销往世界各地的假冒炸弹探测器ADE 651。利奥·本尼迪塔斯在题为《为何有些国家仍使用被定罪的英国老千卖出的假冒炸弹探测器？》的文章中，对仍然相信ADE 651的巴基斯坦官员表示惊讶。他表示，不仅是巴基斯坦，[[伊拉克|伊拉克]]、[[黎巴嫩|黎巴嫩]]、[[肯尼亚|肯尼亚]]和[[泰国|泰国]]的安全部队，不顾美国的一再警告，仍使用ADE 651<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dawn.com/news/858184/lives-at-airport-threatened-by-bogus-bomb-detectors |title=Lives at airport threatened by bogus bomb detectors - - DAWN.COM |accessdate=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2014-06-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140623045834/http://www.dawn.com/news/858184/lives-at-airport-threatened-by-bogus-bomb-detectors |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/shortcuts/2014/jun/09/fake-bomb-detectors-british-conman-pakistan-karachi-airport |title=Why are countries still using the fake bomb detectors sold by a convicted British conman? {{!}} World news {{!}} The Guardian |accessdate=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2014-06-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140624114136/http://www.theguardian.com/world/shortcuts/2014/jun/09/fake-bomb-detectors-british-conman-pakistan-karachi-airport |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2009/11/04/world/middleeast/04sensors.html?_r=0 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2014-04-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140426083438/http://www.nytimes.com/2009/11/04/world/middleeast/04sensors.html?_r=0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。袭击过后，巴基斯坦其他国际机场处于红色警戒状态，安保升级<ref name="FIR"/> ，邻国[[印度|印度]]的机场亦出于高度戒备状态<ref name="zee" />。

一些巴基斯坦官员表示，袭击造成的长远影响，可能使外国航空公司对在巴基斯坦扩大业务表示担忧，已有众多国际航空自2008年起缩减经营范围。目前，有19家国际航空公司服务于巴基斯坦机场<ref name="tribune"/>。6月11日，[[国泰航空|国泰航空]]通知前往卡拉奇的航空临时取消，并密切观察有关情况。同日，鉴于当前局势，[[马尔代夫|马尔代夫]]总统[[阿卜杜拉·亚米恩|阿卜杜拉·亚米恩]]无限期推迟对巴基斯坦的[[国事访问|国事访问]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dawn.com/news/1112030 |title=Cathay Pacific cancels Karachi flights after Taliban attack - World - DAWN.COM |accessdate=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2014-06-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140614225812/http://www.dawn.com/news/1112030 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[爱尔兰|爱尔兰]][[板球|板球]]队原计划2014年9月参加于[[拉合尔|拉合尔]]举行的国际板球比赛，但因袭击而取消。此趟旅程一旦程星，将结束自从2009年[[斯里兰卡|斯里兰卡]]板球队遭到武装分子[[斯里兰卡板球队遇袭事件|袭击]]后，国际板球界对巴基斯坦长达五年的沉寂。这次袭击让巴基斯坦板球委员会最近安排国际球队访问巴基斯坦作出的努力落空<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://tribune.com.pk/story/720352/cricket-pakistan-disappointed-after-ireland-cancel-tour/ |title=Cricket: Pakistan disappointed after Ireland cancel tour following Karachi attack – The Express Tribune<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2014-06-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140621083241/http://tribune.com.pk/story/720352/cricket-pakistan-disappointed-after-ireland-cancel-tour/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="IrelandPakistan">{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/cricket/27800387 |title=Ireland tour to Pakistan called off after Karachi airport attack |accessdate=11 June 2014 |work=BBC Sport |archive-date=2014-06-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140614201502/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/cricket/27800387 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

6月10日，总理纳瓦兹·谢里夫主持召开内阁委员会国家安全会议。出席会议的有陆军主席拉黑尔·谢里夫、内政部长尼萨尔·阿里·乔杜里，及其他政府和军方高级官员<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dawn.com/news/1111808/meeting-on-national-security-under-way-at-pm-house |title=Civil-military leadership discuss internal security - Pakistan |publisher=Dawn.Com |date= |accessdate=2014-06-11 |archive-date=2014-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140610221153/http://www.dawn.com/news/1111808/meeting-on-national-security-under-way-at-pm-house |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

机场和巴基斯坦国际航空蒙受损失达数十亿卢比，估计累计损失超过1800亿卢比<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.thenews.com.pk/Todays-News-3-255226-PIA-suffers-heavy-financial-losses:-officials |title=PIA suffers heavy financial losses: officials - thenews.com.pk |accessdate=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2014-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714150222/http://www.thenews.com.pk/Todays-News-3-255226-PIA-suffers-heavy-financial-losses%3A-officials |dead-url=no }}</ref>。信德省首席总督凯姆·阿里·沙阿宣布对袭击事件的受害者作出赔偿<ref>[http://dunyanews.tv/index.php/en/Pakistan/224836-Karachi-attack-Funeral-prayers-of-martyred-Ranger Karachi attack: Funeral prayers of martyred Rangers, ASF officials offered | Pakistan | Dunya News]</ref>。

=== 塔利班负责 ===
[[巴基斯坦塔利班运动|巴基斯坦塔利班运动]]声称对本次袭击事件负责，宣称袭击是要为2013年11月在[[北瓦济里斯坦|北瓦济里斯坦]]发动的[[无人机|无人机]]袭击中死亡前领袖哈基穆拉·马哈苏德报仇<ref name=ibtimes>{{cite news|last1=Lynch|first1=Dennis|title=Militants Attack Karachi Airport In Pakistan: Live Stream And Updates|url=http://www.ibtimes.com/militants-attack-karachi-airport-pakistan-live-stream-updates-video-1595961|accessdate=8 June 2014|work=[[International_Business_Times|International Business Times]]|date=2014-06-08|archive-date=2014-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140609033643/http://www.ibtimes.com/militants-attack-karachi-airport-pakistan-live-stream-updates-video-1595961|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title='Gunfire resumes' at Karachi airport after deadly raid|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-27758029|publisher=BBC News|accessdate=9 June 2014|date=2014-06-09|archive-date=2018-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181224012158/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-27758029|dead-url=no}}</ref>。塔利班也证实，行凶者来自和塔利班有过亲密合作[[基地组织|基地组织]]分支[[乌兹别克斯坦伊斯兰运动|乌兹别克斯坦伊斯兰运动]]，该组织被包括巴基斯坦在内的一些政府所打击<ref name="Uzbeks"/><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://tribune.com.pk/story/621400/pakistan-bans-three-extremist-outfits-on-orders-from-china/ |title=Pakistan bans three extremist outfits, on orders from China – The Express Tribune |accessdate=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2014-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714184256/http://tribune.com.pk/story/621400/pakistan-bans-three-extremist-outfits-on-orders-from-china/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。塔利班发言人沙希德将本次袭击描述为塔利班和伊斯兰运动的联合行动<ref name="Uzbeks"/>。伊斯兰运动在网上声明中证实其在袭击中担任的角色，声称要报复巴基斯坦对乌兹别克人和其他境外武装采取的军事行动<ref name="Reuters">{{Cite web |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/06/11/us-pakistan-militants-idUSKBN0EM14L20140611 |title=Feared Uzbek Jihadists behind deadly Pakistan airport attack {{!}} Reuters |accessdate=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2014-06-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140621131734/http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/06/11/us-pakistan-militants-idUSKBN0EM14L20140611 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，还提供了十名参与机场袭击的乌兹别克“战士”的照片。照片中的武装分子身着绿色长袍和白色运动鞋，手持冲锋枪，约20岁出头，照片拍攝地點似乎在山区<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nation.com.pk/national/11-Jun-2014/islamic-movement-of-uzbekistan-takes-responsibility-for-karachi-airport-terror-attack |title=Islamic Movement of Uzbekistan takes responsibility for Karachi airport terror attack |accessdate=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2014-06-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140618061537/http://www.nation.com.pk/national/11-Jun-2014/islamic-movement-of-uzbekistan-takes-responsibility-for-karachi-airport-terror-attack |dead-url=no }}</ref>。巴基斯坦防务分析家伊姆蒂亚兹·古尔分析，美军2001年[[阿富汗战争_(2001年)|入侵]]后，伊斯兰运动在内的境外势力逃离阿富汗，活跃于阿富汗边境的部落地区。他们享受着塔利班提供的保护和住处，为塔利班的行动提供步兵<ref name="Uzbeks"/>。乌兹别克武装分子先前曾参与在巴基斯坦发动的大规模袭击，包括2012年[[白沙瓦|白沙瓦]][[巴查·汗国际机场|巴查·汗国际机场]]袭击和2011年卡拉奇迈赫兰空军基地袭击，并分别在2012年和2013年帮助本努和德拉·伊斯梅尔·汗越狱<ref name="Uzbeks2">{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-27790892|title=Karachi airport: Islamic Movement of Uzbekistan claims attack|work=BBC|date=11 June 2014|accessdate=11 June 2014|archive-date=2014-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140614202308/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-27790892|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.thenews.com.pk/Todays-News-2-255982-Who-are-the-Uzbeks-launching-terror-strikes-in-Pakistan |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2014-08-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140808104026/http://www.thenews.com.pk/Todays-News-2-255982-Who-are-the-Uzbeks-launching-terror-strikes-in-Pakistan |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

塔利班指挥官阿卜杜拉·巴哈尔驳回巴基斯坦政府就“战争工具”的最新和谈要求，提及巴方打击武装分子的空袭行动，声称巴政府杀害“数百名部族妇女儿童”。他还警告，将有更多针对国家的袭击<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://gulfnews.com/news/world/pakistan/karachi-airport-cleared-of-militants-after-attack-kills-28-1.1344670 |title=Karachi airport cleared of militants after attack kills 28 {{!}} GulfNews.com |accessdate=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2014-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140615214620/http://gulfnews.com/news/world/pakistan/karachi-airport-cleared-of-militants-after-attack-kills-28-1.1344670 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=autogenerated1>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ibtimes.com/pakistani-taliban-leader-says-plan-was-hijack-plane-karachi-airport-warns-worse-attacks-1596004 |title=Pakistani Taliban Leader Says Plan Was To Hijack A Plane At Karachi Airport, Warns Of 'Worse Attacks' |accessdate=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2014-06-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140620132429/http://www.ibtimes.com/pakistani-taliban-leader-says-plan-was-hijack-plane-karachi-airport-warns-worse-attacks-1596004 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

塔利班发言人沙希德解释针对机场的原因：“我们选的位置会造成平民死很少、官员死很多。”沙希德警告，组织将参与从6月10日起针对巴基斯坦政府的全面战争。”但是，“若巴基斯坦现在作出避让，”沙希德表示，“我们已做好进行有意义对话战备<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2014/06/09/world/asia/pakistan-karachi-airport-attacks/index.html?hpt=hp_t1 |title=7 more bodies found after Pakistan airport terrorist attack - CNN.com |accessdate=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2014-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140612151829/http://edition.cnn.com/2014/06/09/world/asia/pakistan-karachi-airport-attacks/index.html?hpt=hp_t1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。”他补充，“这次袭击的主要目的是破坏政府，包括劫持飞机和损毁国家设施<ref name="zee">{{cite news|url=http://zeenews.india.com/news/south-asia/karachi-airport-siege-live-pakistan-taliban-own-up-to-attack_938093.html|title=Jinnah International Airport is live and back, says Pakistan's Civil Aviation Authority|work=Zee News|date=10 June 2014|accessdate=10 June 2014|archive-date=2014-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140611235923/http://zeenews.india.com/news/south-asia/karachi-airport-siege-live-pakistan-taliban-own-up-to-attack_938093.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”

=== 军方行动 ===
6月10日，巴基斯坦安全部队对靠近阿富汗边境的西北部落地区[[开伯尔特区|开伯尔特区]]迪拉村进行空中打击，9处藏身点内25名武装分子被击毙。此次打击在袭击过后开展，是过去数月军事行动的延伸<ref name="25 militants">{{Cite web |url=http://tribune.com.pk/story/719855/aerial-bombing-in-tirah-valley-kills-15-militants/ |title=Aerial bombing in Tirah valley kills 25 militants – The Express Tribune |accessdate=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2018-06-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180613090226/https://tribune.com.pk/story/719855/aerial-bombing-in-tirah-valley-kills-15-militants/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。该地区公认为[[中亚|中亚]]境外恐怖势力和数个反国激进派别份子的容身之处<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dawn.com/news/1111785/at-least-25-killed-in-airstrikes-in-tirah-valley |title=At least 25 killed in airstrikes in Tirah valley - Pakistan - DAWN.COM |accessdate=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2014-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140610213950/http://www.dawn.com/news/1111785/at-least-25-killed-in-airstrikes-in-tirah-valley |dead-url=no }}</ref>。防务分析家认为，卡拉奇的机场袭击在背后推动了[[伊斯兰堡|伊斯兰堡]]与武装分子目前的和谈，导致北瓦济里斯坦和阿富汗边境部落地区的全面军事进攻。据一名巴基斯坦安全官员表示，“军方已做好行动准备，一切取决于政府决议<ref>{{cite news|url=http://online.wsj.com/articles/gunmen-attack-karachi-airport-1402301470|title=Pakistan Weighs Strike Against Taliban Over Airport Attack|first=Saeed|last=Shah|work=Wall Street Journal|accessdate=2014-06-21|archive-date=2014-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140612001256/http://online.wsj.com/articles/gunmen-attack-karachi-airport-1402301470|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”6月11日，军方在[[拉瓦尔品第|拉瓦尔品第]]总司令部召开最高军事指挥官会议，决定加强对武装分子藏身点的空袭<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dawn.com/news/1112021/ |title=Army resolves to intensify air strikes against militants - Pakistan - DAWN.COM |accessdate=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2014-06-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140621220047/http://www.dawn.com/news/1112021 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

6月12日凌晨，美国于巴基斯坦西北部部落地区的无人机战役休整6个月后，在北瓦济里斯坦靠近米拉姆沙阿一带，连续两次发动无人机袭击，16名武装分子嫌疑人被击毙。巴基斯坦情报来源，声称被击毙的武装分子中包括四名乌兹别克人、几名阿富汗塔利班指挥官和关键成员和两名巴基斯坦塔利班运动[[旁遮普邦|旁遮普邦]]份子<ref name="drone">{{Cite web |url=http://www.dawn.com/news/1112050 |title=Successive drone strikes leave at least 16 dead in N Waziristan - Pakistan - DAWN.COM<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2018-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612162555/https://www.dawn.com/news/1112050 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dawn.com/news/1112253 |title=Drone targeted Haqqani network commander, Afghan Taliban: sources - Pakistan - DAWN.COM<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2014-07-17 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6R8SEsghG?url=http://www.dawn.com/news/1112253 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

6月15日，[[巴基斯坦空军|巴基斯坦空军]]用战斗机轰炸北瓦济里斯坦八处恐怖分子窝点，安全官员透露，至少击毙105名武装分子<ref name="105 militants">{{Cite web |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/06/15/us-pakistan-airstrikes-idUSKBN0EQ0F720140615 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2014-06-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140621131709/http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/06/15/us-pakistan-airstrikes-idUSKBN0EQ0F720140615 |dead-url=no }}</ref>（官方统计为150名<ref name="150 militants"/>），由于主要目标为乌兹别克人藏身点，击毙者大多为乌兹别克战士，数名武装分子与机场袭击关联<ref name="150 militants">{{Cite web |url=http://www.dawn.com/news/1112875/mostly-uzbeks-killed-in-overnight-n-waziristan-bombing-army |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2018-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612162315/https://www.dawn.com/news/1112875/mostly-uzbeks-killed-in-overnight-n-waziristan-bombing-army |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此前有军事情报来源，确认军事行动存在外国和当地武装分子藏身点。乌兹别克武装分子指挥官、机场袭击主谋阿布·阿卜杜勒·阿赫曼·阿玛尼，据称被击毙。中国西部[[维吾尔族|维吾尔]]分裂主义集团[[东突厥斯坦伊斯兰运动|东突厥斯坦伊斯兰运动]]的数名外国武装分子亦被击毙<ref name="Almani">{{Cite web |url=http://www.dawn.com/news/1112901/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2019-04-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190416093309/https://www.dawn.com/news/1112901 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同日，巴基斯坦军方正式宣布军事战略，旨在搜捕窝藏于北瓦济里斯坦的国内外武装分子。三军公共关系局发言人阿西姆·巴杰瓦少将发表声明：“借助北瓦济里斯坦的基地，这些恐怖分子曾发动针对巴基斯坦政府的战争，从各个方面破坏我们国家的生活，延缓经济的增长，造成生命财产上的巨大损失。我们英勇的军队一直致力于消灭这些恐怖份子，不论他们的色调如何，藏身所在何处。伴随全国的支持，及与其他国家执法机构的协调，这些国家敌人将在全国范围内没有容身之处<ref name="Zarb">{{Cite web |url=http://www.dawn.com/news/1112909/pakistan-launches-zarb-e-azb-military-operation-in-n-waziristan |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-06-22 |archive-date=2014-08-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140808015944/http://www.dawn.com/news/1112909/pakistan-launches-zarb-e-azb-military-operation-in-n-waziristan |dead-url=no }}</ref>。”

=== 国内情况 ===
离机场袭击仅仅两天的6月10日，两到四名身份不明的武装分子在机场安全部队学院开火后撤退。学院所在贫民区被视为犯罪分子的枢纽。警察和别动队员早在2011年就曾在该地发动多次空袭进行定点清除<ref name="Goth">{{Cite web |url=http://www.dawn.com/news/1111801/ |title=Sharjeel lambasts Nawaz govt over Karachi attack handling - Pakistan - DAWN.COM |accessdate=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2014-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140616214255/http://www.dawn.com/news/1111801 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 。安全部队随后在该地展开搜捕行动，其间有两人被拘留<ref name="FIR"/>。袭击事件中没有人员伤亡报告，围栏未遭破坏。真纳国际机场航班停飞，其他航班在機場恢复通航前被分流至其他城市。信德省别动队总干事认为该袭击旨在制造恐慌。[[巴基斯坦塔利班运动|塔利班]]声称对事件负责<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thenews.com.pk/article-150330-Terrorists-open-fire-near-ASF-Academy |title=Terrorists open fire near ASF Academy |publisher=Thenews.com.pk |date= |accessdate=2014-06-11 |archive-date=2014-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140610175107/http://www.thenews.com.pk/article-150330-Terrorists-open-fire-near-ASF-Academy |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dawn.com/news/1111791 |title=TTP claims attack on Karachi ASF camp - Pakistan |publisher=Dawn.Com |date= |accessdate=2014-06-11 |archive-date=2014-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140610202427/http://www.dawn.com/news/1111791 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

这次袭击引发巴基斯坦社交媒体的广泛反映，受到政客、记者和社会科学家的谴责<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dawn.com/news/1111570 |title=Attack on Karachi airport: Reactions on social media - Pakistan - DAWN.COM |accessdate=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2014-06-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140620224348/http://www.dawn.com/news/1111570 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。巴基斯坦对事件反响强烈，各大媒体质疑政府试图与虎谋皮，对此类袭击失策，敏感设施安全存疑，众多评论员呼吁对武装分子采用新的行动安全设备<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-27779474 |title=BBC News - Pakistani media demand action over airport attack |accessdate=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2014-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140615055825/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-27779474 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。巴基斯坦司法运动党主席伊姆兰·汗及反对党主要领导者，谴责袭击事件，并严厉批评政府，要求高级官员辞职。他指出：“这是政府的完全失策，国家竭力保护重要设施和公民的生命安全，那些对此事坐视不理的人，必须立马承担责任并辞职<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://tribune.com.pk/story/719767/taftan-bombing-karachi-airport-attack-pti-asks-top-officials-to-step-down/ |title=Taftan bombing, Karachi airport attack: PTI asks top officials to step down – The Express Tribune |accessdate=2014-06-21 |archive-date=2014-06-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140614190133/http://tribune.com.pk/story/719767/taftan-bombing-karachi-airport-attack-pti-asks-top-officials-to-step-down/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。”[[巴基斯坦国民议会|巴基斯坦国民议会]]通过一项谴责袭击的决议<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thenews.com.pk/article-150334-National-Assembly-passes-resolutions-condemning-attacks-in-Karachi-Taftan- |title=National Assembly passes resolutions condemning attacks in Karachi, Taftan |publisher=Thenews.com.pk |date= |accessdate=2014-06-11 |archive-date=2014-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140610214055/http://www.thenews.com.pk/article-150334-National-Assembly-passes-resolutions-condemning-attacks-in-Karachi-Taftan- |dead-url=no }}</ref>。信德省新闻部长梅蒙批评联邦政府对袭击事件发生失策，将袭击列入军方及安全机构的档案<ref name="Goth"/>。

